menu.anonymous_about_desc: All of this born from a deeply rooted love for games, utmost care about customers, and a belief that you should own the things you buy.
menu.anonymous_about_header: GOG.com is a digital distribution platform – an online store with a curated selection of games, an optional gaming client giving you freedom of choice, and a vivid community of gamers.
menu.cart_reminder: There's something waiting for you inside!
menu.connect_about_description: It’s our unique initiative which allows you to add selected games from your Steam library to your GOG.com account for FREE! Learn more
menu.connect_button: SEE ALL GAMES AVAILABLE IN GOG CONNECT
menu.connect_header: %boldStart%8 NEW GAMES ADDED%boldEnd% TO GOG CONNECT
menu.connect_new_games_description: Limbo, Fallout 3, Fallout New Vegas, The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim, Assassin’s Creed 2, Assassin’s Creed Brotherhood, Assassin’s Creed Revelations and Assassin’s Creed 3.
menu.dragons_dogma_description: Gather your party and venture into this monster-hunting epic! Here there be fearsome beasts, that only your careful customization and smart co-operation can cut down to size.
menu.features_slider_1: [[boldStart]]Hand-picking the best in gaming.[[boldEnd]] A selection of great games, from modern hits to all-time classics, that you really shouldn’t miss.
menu.features_slider_2: [[boldStart]]Customer-first approach.[[boldEnd]] Delivering user-friendly support enriched with additional customer benefits.
menu.features_slider_3: [[boldStart]]Gamer-friendly platform.[[boldEnd]] We’re here to make a difference in the way you buy and play your games, giving you freedom of choice and a hassle-free experience.
menu.feedback_header: Share your feedback about %newLine% our new navigation
menu.feedback_thanks_message: Thank you! We really value your feedback as it helps us a lot. Please, feel free to share your thoughts with us everytime you want.
menu.friend_list_empty_description: Play, chat, and share experiences with your friends on GOG.com
menu.full_throttle_description: Over 20 years after it’s original release, classic point-and-click adventure - %boldStart%Full Throttle%boldEnd% - is back in a remastered edition featuring all new hand-drawn and 3D high-resolution artwork, with remastered audio and music.
menu.gog_galaxy_about: %boldStart%GOG GALAXY is a fully optional client%boldEnd% to install, play and update your games. It also offers online multiplayer, achievements, chat, game-time tracking and more - but it’s up to you which features you want to use.
menu.gog_galaxy_os_other: Get it for Windows and macOS
menu.gog_galaxy_whats_new: Learn what’s new and improved in version 1.1
menu.guardians_of_the_galaxy_descripiton: A brand new story of the universe’s unlikeliest heroes: Star-Lord, Gamora, Drax, Rocket, and Groot. In the wake of an epic battle, the Guardians discover an artifact of unspeakable power.%newLine% %boldStart%Episode 1 is available now!%boldEnd%
menu.gwent_description: When every card counts, winning is a matter of skill, wit, and strategy — not luck.
menu.hellblade_description: A stunning journey into the shattered mind of a Celtic warrior seeking revenge for her fallen lover.
menu.little_nightmares_description: %boldStart%Pre-order Little Nightmares, %newLine%get INSIDE right now!%boldEnd%%newLine%%newLine% Immerse yourself in %boldStart%Little Nightmares%boldEnd%, a dark whimsical tale that will confront you with your childhood fears.
menu.may_the_4th_sale_title: The best Star Wars™ games the galaxy has to offer
menu.notifications_empty_description: Se nye chatbeskjeder, venneinvitasjoner, og viktige annonseringer og tilbud som er relevante for deg
menu.on_sale_button: Bla i alle spill som er på salg for tiden
menu.outlast_description: %boldStart%Outlast 2%boldEnd% will have you running scared from the horrors spawned by bloody fanaticism and twisted superstition. How long will you last?
menu.search_no_results_found_description: Try adjusting the terms of your search, you can search by game titles, publishers, and developers.
menu.sports_racing_button: Bla i alle sport- og bil-spill
menu.tacoma_description: From the visionary creators of Gone Home, comes a multi-pathed story experience that you can explore at your own pace. Who were Tacoma's six crew members and how did each of them deal with the crisis that engulfed the enigmatic space station?
